Circular Charts

Circular charts are a nice way to display informations. The values go from 5 to 100, with an increment of 5 each time.

File to include

@include "components/circular-charts";

Not animated

<div class="circular-chart circular-5 no-anim">
    <svg class="circle-chart" viewbox="0 0 33.83098862 33.83098862" width="100" height="100">
            <circle class="circular-chart-background" style="cx: 16.91549431; cy: 16.91549431; r: 15.91549431;" />
            <circle class="circular-chart-circle" style="cx: 16.91549431; cy: 16.91549431; r: 15.91549431;" />
            <g class="circular-chart-info">
                <text class="circular-chart-number" x="16.91549431" y="16.5" alignment-baseline="central" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8">
                    5%
                </text>
            </g>
    </svg>
</div>

<div class="circular-chart circular-15 no-anim">
